OL,3,CIt's a Merry Christmas for Wales'
OL,4,COldest man after receiving trolley of
OL,5,Cgifts
OL,7,FWales' oldest man has been given a
OL,8,FChristmas treat by staff at his local
OL,9,Fsupermarket which he's visited almost
OL,10,Fevery day in the last 24 years.
OL,12,FOwen Filer, 106, has received a
OL,13,Ftrolley full of presents from Asda's
OL,14,FCwmbran store to say thank you for
OL,15,Fbeing such a loyal customer.
OL,17,FThe trolley included festive gifts
OL,18,Flike biscuits, yule log and mince pies
OL,19,Fas well as some of his regular
OL,20,Fpurchases.
