OL,3,CIt's a Merry Christmas for Wales'
OL,4,COldest man after receiving trolley of
OL,5,Cgifts
OL,7,FMr Filer who's become Wales' most
OL,8,Ffamous centenarian for his great wit
OL,9,Fand incredible physical health for his
OL,10,Fage, turned 106-years-old in October.
OL,12,FHe was born when David Lloyd George
OL,13,Fwas Prime Minister and George V was
OL,14,FKing. Since then, he has seen 21 other
OL,15,Foccupants of Number 10 and four other
OL,16,Fmonarchs.
OL,18,FHe became so recognisable in Wales and
OL,19,Fworldwide after he stopped an ITV news
OL,20,Fcrew in Newport revealing he was 100
OL,21,Fin 2020, but they didn't believe him.
