OL,4,COldest man after receiving trolley of
OL,5,Cgifts
OL,7,FDuring Mr Filer's long life he served
OL,8,Fin the Royal Welsh Fusiliers and then
OL,9,Fthe Military Police during the Second
OL,10,FWorld War.
OL,12,FHe recently met King Charles at a VJ
OL,13,FDay anniversary in August at the
OL,14,FNational Memorial Arboretum in
OL,15,FAlrewas, Staffordshire.
