OL,4,COldest man after receiving trolley of
OL,5,Cgifts
OL,7,FCali Beale, Asda Cwmbran's customer
OL,8,Fmanager, says everyone in the store
OL,9,Floves seeing Mr Filer, who has been
OL,10,Fdescribed as a "local celebrity".
OL,12,FShe said: "Mr Filer is a true
OL,13,Fgentleman and it's an honour to have
OL,14,Fhim in our store.
OL,16,F"He loves his Asda shopping trips and
OL,17,Fenjoys chatting to the girls on
OL,18,Fcheckouts.
